name: Franklin ClearBridge Sustainable International Growth Fund
longDescription: In pursuing its investment objective, the underlying fund may invest up to 15 percent of its assets in equity securities of issuers in emerging markets; may invest in China A-securities directly through Stock Connect; seeks to identify for inclusion in the funds portfolio equity securities that offer above-average growth potential and trade at a significant discount to the funds sub-advisors assessment of their intrinsic value. Franklin ClearBridge Sustainable International Growth Active ETF seeks to provide longterm capital appreciation through exposure to international equity securities.
